text: Kahlgrund Fighters or RWG Mömbris-Königshofen is a wrestling team in Germany. In the 2010-2011 season, the team came in second place, at the top level of German wrestling, Ringer-Bundesliga. In the 2025/26 season, the team will compete in the Hessen Landesliga.https://www.liga- db.de/nvligendb.asp?WCI=Std&FID;=200&SLID;=1186&fem;=0. Retrieved 2025-03-31 That league is two levels below the Hessen Oberliga. ==History== 2024/25 season: The team placed first, in the Hessen Verbandsliga.https://www.liga- db.de/nvligendb.asp?WCI=Std&FID;=5&fem;=0&SLID;=1136. Retrieved 2025-03-31 The members that won the most points were Florian Lamm, followed by Zakri Visinhiriiev and Iustin Mosneaga.https://kahlgrund-fighters.de/. Retrieved 2025-03-31 2016/17 season: The team placed first, in the Hessen Oberliga; The team chose to not be moved to the (level or) division above, the 2.
